data.description: $70,000 PRICE REDUCTION! WOW! WOW! WOW! ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN 4.125%!  160 fully fenced acres  plus home and detached structures for under $480k????? YES that's correct!! Not a typo!!!! Lovely ranch style home in the heart of Estancia Valley! Main level constructed of 12'' concrete block with rebar! home built with thermo-insulation!  Sits on 160 acres of grazing land, fully fenced and cross fenced! Well for livestock (5/1/2020) w/solar pump-great producing well!   700 gallon stock tanks, (4) 2 cattle pens.  Three phase power possible! Large detached barn with loft and extra storage!  If  peace and quiet away from the city is what you're looking for this is it. Country living at its best well worth the drive.
